{"tid":1357991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗巴打想大家一齊入去呢個page幫手","createTime":"2019-07-24T00:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T15:00:43.000Z","uid":120786,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"957f3596d4523a42c2af7ef00c975488eaef1e9d","tid":1357991,"uid":120786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:04:57.000Z","msg":"大家好，我係一個自細係元朗長大，安居樂業嘅巴打，星期日發生嘅事令我覺得好心痛，令我自己對元朗嘅信心跌到落谷低。元朗呢個地方由細到大我都覺得元朗好好住，好安全，依家我連去西鐵站果邊都唔敢去，就算平時搭巴士係東頭村站落都唔敢，特登係又新街落行，我想同大家一齊守衛元朗，我覺得依家我地做到嘅第一件事就係去盡在元朗個page拎元朗居民嘅心，呢個page係元朗最多人睇嘅page，但係好多留言係吹緊另一邊風向，我自己成日睇到好心寒，明明我自己身邊嘅朋友風向都唔會咁......如果有中立或者對時事唔多了解嘅人好易俾佢地帶到風向，到時元朗遊行起訴無咁易令普通居民反感，要點做同要點樣留言大家可以一齊係度討論下！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/WoYuenLong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWoYuenLong%2F&d=usS1U3EkKACzPkxZ%2FEkdU%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=0e77ce0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/WoYuenLong/</a><br />\n<br />\n一個元朗人上<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5BTS7AT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5BTS7AT.png&h=960c1b90&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1500f2d04e4418b4d0bfe4b60f0915073e4ce058","tid":1357991,"uid":120786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:11:13.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"119edb8c9f272bba69182aa2133e8e5e67655f88","tid":1357991,"uid":120786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:21:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"179bd35ea35b6a7b1722070296af4357299f175d","tid":1357991,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T01:24:23.000Z","msg":"支持你<br />\n有follow"},{"pid":"84f88408cf3f0154dec886445ddc0bd6a4fa7039","tid":1357991,"uid":120786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:33:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"829830ca85d7b1ba179a44bcd440a771cdb1d2a0","tid":1357991,"uid":120786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:00:43.000Z","msg":"推